| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4517 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8aefdad3-b85c-5e59-b7ba-ca990d581e06"
